<html>
<body>
<h1>It's time to play: Battle!</h1>
<h4><%=@game.player_1.name%> vs <%=@game.player_2.name%></h4>

<p><%=@game.current_turn.name%> is now in control</p>

<p> Current points: 
<ul>
<li><%=@game.player_1.name%>: <%=@game.player_1.points%>HP </li>
<li><%=@game.player_2.name%>: <%=@game.player_2.points%>HP </li>
</ul>
</p>


<p> Press the attack button to attack your opponent </p>
<form type="attack" action="/attack">
<button>Attack</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>